Description: This 335 is a beauty, rings nicely acoustically and has been professionally set-up. It is in excellent condition with some minor surface marks here and there: a slight surface scratch near the bridge volume pot, a couple of light marks from a tuner at the top of the headstock, a slight surface scratch that can't be felt higher up on the neck and a couple of minor indentations that are difficult to find at the bottom of the back, likely from my stand. While I wanted to note everything I could find, overall the guitar looks and feels brand new. Comes with all case candy including Certificate of Authenticity. Full specs and more information can be found on the Gibson site:http://www.gibson.com/Products/Electric-Guitars/2016/Memphis/ES-335.aspx
